{
  "doc_id": "7903",
  "text": "From the analytical point of view, the existence of solutions to (3.3) has not been proved, yet. The main result in [CITATION_1] only states that (3.3) can be rigorously obtained as the limit of systems of n × n conservation laws describing n populations of vehicles, each characterized by their maximal speed.",
